review_text: Exactly what I wanted. A very good introduction to how to develop AI workshops and agents.

I really enjoyed this course! It provided a solid introduction to AI agents and workflows, explaining the core concepts clearly while also showing practical applications. I especially appreciated how it laid the foundation for building agentic systems and opened my eyes to the possibilities they offer. A great balance of theory and practice.
Overall the course is really good. It's understandable that it can not cover every corner in such short time.

Max always makes complex topics easy to understand. Although this course was shorter than many of Max's other courses, I feel like I now have a good understanding of AI Agents and that I have enough information to start working on my own agents.
I am full stack developer I followed your other course, this course is my first step for AI, gave me understanding and confidence to keep learning Generative AI, Thank you.

As usual Max's course was excellent. I really appreciate him going into detail with the coding before showing us how to do the same with SDKs. His instructing manner is just at the right pace and very thoriugh and detailed.
Very good course.

As I’m trying to understand what an AI Agent is, this course was helpful and gave me a clear idea of the different ways it can be implemented. I recommend this course to anyone who is beginning to explore AI Agents.

Excellent course for learning and understanding ai agents in python. I have gone from not having a clue to understanding what they are, how they work and how to use them. If you are looking for step by step instructions, this is not the course for you. If you are looking for a detailed overview and understanding of what they are and an idea of how they work...Bingo......If you understand Python, you will grasp this every easily and feel confident to move onto you next course. Cheers Max!

When I saw this was made by Max, I was so relived. He is awesome understanding how to focus the course into what's important without having to talk about external things like business or developer fundamentals. If you are already a developer, this is the one for you.

Max nails it again. This is a great course for developers who want to understand how the "agent platforms" work under the hood. I have watched countless hours of tutorials on MCP servers and what not, but never understood how exactly the tool calls worked. Max has explained in this course exactly how you can write your own agent from ground up. Although a basic one, it's still very useful to understand the core concept behind AI agents.
Really good approach showing how to do it without any framework (langchain, crewai) and then introducing CrewAi, that really helped.

Max presents the topics in a clear and engaging manner. Although this is an overview course, it seems to touch upon the key areas that are important to set the foundation for additional research and study. I feel this is a really great course and has great value. I will note that there are a bunch of example files that are used in the course that are not included in the code downloadable from github. It would be easy for Max to provide such files as they don't need to be large, but they are not present. That is a disappointment.
This is my first course for learning generative AI, I found it very helpful to understand on high level how Generative AI works under the hood.
Great, short introduction to what can be done using LLMs for automation - that's what I was expecting to get.

An excellent and beautifully designed course. The structure is very thoughtful, whenever a topic initially felt less engaging or out of place, the following lecture immediately clarified its purpose and relevance. Overall, it’s well-organized, insightful, and highly recommended as an entry-level course for anyone looking to get started with LLMs and AI Agents.
